<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <title>Large 라벨</title>
    <style>
      @page {
        size: 100mm 100mm;
        margin: 0;
      }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: 'Nanum Gothic', sans-serif;
        height: 100%;
      }
      .label-content {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
      }
      h1, h2, p {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      /* Large 라벨 스타일 */
      .label-large {
        width: 100%;
        height: 100%;
        padding: 10px 14px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-size: 9pt;
        line-height: 1.4;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        justify-content: space-between;
      }

      .large-top {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-start;
      }
      
      .large-title {
        font-size: 16pt;
        font-weight: bold;
      }
      
      .frozen-badge {
        border: 1.5px solid #000;
        border-radius: 6px;
        padding: 4px;
        width: 60px;
        height: 60px;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 7pt;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
      }
      
      .frozen-badge svg {
        width: 28px;
        height: 28px;
        margin-bottom: 2px;
      }

      .large-info p {
        margin: 2px 0;
        text-align: left;
      }

      .large-bottom {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: flex-end;
      }
      
      .barcode-box {
        text-align: center;
      }
      
      .barcode-box img {
        width: 140px;
        height: auto;
      }
      
      .date-box {
        text-align: left;
        font-size: 10pt;
      }
      
      .microwave-box {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 8pt;
      }
      
      .microwave-box svg {
        display: block;
        width: 42px;
        height: 28px;
        margin: 0 auto 2px auto;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="label-content">
      <div class="label-large">
        <!-- 상단: 제품명 + 냉동 배지 -->
        <div class="large-top">
          <div class="large-title"><%= productName %></div>
          <div class="frozen-badge">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
              <path d="M32 8v48M8 32h48M16 16l32 32M48 16L16 48"/>
            </svg>
            냉동식품
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- 본문 -->
        <div class="large-info">
          <p>등록번호: 제IIIRAX0009호 / 제품명: <%= productName %></p>
          <p>종류 및 형태: 단미사료 / 혼합성-혼합제 / 큐브</p>
          <p>성분량: 조단백질 36% 이상, 조지방 25% 이하, 조회분 5% 이하, 조섬유 5% 이하, 수분 10% 이하</p>
          <p>원료의 명칭: 쌀, 계란, 두부, 브로콜리, 당근, 닭가슴살, 단호박, 코코넛오일</p>
          <p>실제중량: 50g</p>
          <p>사료의 용도: 애완동물용</p>
          <p>제조일자: 유통기한으로부터 12개월 전</p>
          <p>주의사항: 반려동물 이외에는 급여하지 마십시오.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- 하단: 바코드 + 날짜 + 전자레인지 -->
        <div class="large-bottom">
          <div class="barcode-box">
            <img src="data:image/png;base64,<%= barcodeBase64 %>" alt="Barcode" />
            <div>8 800278 470831</div>
          </div>
          <div class="date-box">
            <p>제조일자: <%= manufactureDate %></p>
            <p>유통기한: <%= expiryDate %></p>
            <p>제품수량: 10개</p>
          </div>
          <div class="microwave-box">
            <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 64 48" fill="none" stroke="#000" stroke-width="2">
              <rect x="2" y="8" width="52" height="32" rx="2"/>
              <circle cx="58" cy="16" r="2"/>
              <circle cx="58" cy="24" r="2"/>
              <circle cx="58" cy="32" r="2"/>
            </svg>
            30초~2분
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>

